title: Easy Virtue, False Charity: Somaly Mam, Tyra Banks, Oprah & Susan Sarandon.
description:
Shout out to Tyra Banks.  Shout out to Al Jazeera: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iiy51eU_yCA
The charity Somaly Mam created, AFESIP, still exists.  If you google around you'll find they're still promoting themselves, and still seeking donations, around the internet, whereas the (separate) foundation Somaly Mam named after herself ceased to exist.  Read more if you want to know more: https://www.newsweek.com/2014/05/30/somaly-mam-holy-saint-and-sinner-sex-trafficking-251642.html
